'''Droidfest''' was an annual used-[[Droid/Legends|droid]] sale on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] supported by the combined effort of the [[Jawa Droid Traders]]. An outward version of the annual intra-Jawa [[swap meet]]s, Droidfest attracted a seedy collection of fringers looking to purchase cheap droids. In the Droidfest of [[5 ABY/Legends|5 ABY]], [[Ken]], [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]], [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] and [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] purchased [[KT-18]].

